---
title: Roasted Broccoli
tags: vegetable, kid-friendly, quick and easy
servings: 4
cook time: 25 minutes
ai_image: true
date added: 2026-03-17
---

Preheat oven to 425°F. Spread @Costco broccoli florets{1%lb} in a single layer on a #rimmed baking sheet{}. Drizzle with @olive oil{2%tbsp}, season with @salt{} and @black pepper{}, and toss to coat. Roast until florets are tender and the edges are lightly charred, about ~{20%minutes}. Serve immediately.
